<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rise Beyond 2 - Movie Review</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #f1f5f9;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #1e293b;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .movie-cover {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid #334155;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .rating-box {
            background: #334155;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        h2 {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #38bdf8;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        li {
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
        }

        li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        strong {
            color: #f8fafc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main>
        <h1>Rise Beyond 2</h1>

        <img 
            src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/rise-beyond-2.png" 
            alt="A cinematic poster showing a lone explorer overlooking a futuristic neon-lit cityscape" 
            class="movie-cover"
        >

        <p class="description">
            In a world where gravity is a luxury, one explorer must journey to the edge of the atmosphere to save the last remnants of civilization. A breathtaking sequel that defies expectations.
        </p>

        <p class="rating-box">
            <strong>Movie Rating:</strong> 
            <span aria-hidden="true">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐☆</span> 
            (9.2/10)
        </p>

        <h2>Cast Members</h2>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>James Holloway</strong> as Ethan Carter</li>
            <li><strong>Sarah Jenkins</strong> as Commander Lyra</li>
            <li><strong>Marcus Vane</strong> as The Architect</li>
            <li><strong>Elena Rossi</strong> as Maya</li>
        </ul>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
